data.description: Great location close to 1-40, shopping and medical center. 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths with a 1/2 bath downstairs. Huge primary bedroom with enough space for a king size bed and a sitting area. Upstairs has a large den with a walk in closet that can make a quiet homework nook or home office. Off the den is the laundry room with built in cabinets and built in ironing board. 2 bedrooms upstairs each with walk in closets and full bath with large linen. Downstairs has a wonderful great room with defined dining and living spaces.  Kitchen has great cabinet space and pantry. There is a 2-car garage with the entrance off the back of the house. Backyard is fenced with a patio. The heating/air is new, replaced in 2022. Vinyl flooring upstairs added 2022. New gas water heater replaced 2021. Living spaces downstairs freshly painted along with upstairs den and primary bedroom in 2024.  Prime neighborhood location near a large playground and basketball court. Community pool included in HOA dues.
